<p>The minimum duration of a press for it to be recognized as a long
press gesture, in milliseconds.</p><p>A value of -1 will make the <link xref="Clutter.ClickAction">Clutter.ClickAction</link> use the value of
the <link xref="Clutter.Settings-long-press-duration">Clutter.Settings:long-press-duration</link> property.</p>
